<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1944639-for-those-who-have-read-the-book---do-you">For those who have read the book - do you think the ending is real? Or is Unwin dreaming again. Though not knowing the ending is the hallmark of good surrealism.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1944639'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F4135863-the-manual-of-detection">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
