</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/1944639-for-those-who-have-read-the-book---do-you">Add your answer</a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>

</div>
<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/1012174-kristie"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1609643996i/1012174._UX100_CR0,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/1012174-kristie">Kristie</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
I think the ending is real. But also, I think Sivart was asleep for too long, and Hoffman either partially merged with him or took him over.
</span>
</div>
